OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777835461
OL,3,CTelecomms engineer paid foreigner to
OL,4,Cabuse children
OL,6,FBeckett, 37, from Wakefield, pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to 25 charges at Leeds Crown
OL,8,FCourt and was jailed for 16 years,
OL,9,Fwith an extended licence period of
OL,10,Fseven years.
OL,12,FDanielle Pownall, of the National
OL,13,FCrime Agency, said: "This was a long
OL,14,Fand complex investigation into a
OL,15,Fdepraved individual with a blatant
OL,16,Fdisregard for children.
OL,18,F"Beckett completely dehumanised his
OL,19,Fvictims, paying pitiful amounts of
OL,20,Fmoney in exchange for images and
OL,21,Fvideos of extreme child abuse."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777835461
OL,3,CTelecomms engineer paid foreigner to
OL,4,Cabuse children
OL,6,FBeckett was arrested in December 2022
OL,7,Fafter the NCA received intelligence
OL,8,Ffrom international partners.
OL,10,FInvestigators found links between a
OL,11,FPayPal account, Gmail account and
OL,12,Fmobile number used by Beckett.
OL,14,FThe NCA said he "exploited the
OL,15,Ffacilitator and victims' financial
OL,16,Fsituation" by offering payments from
OL,17,Flittle as #6.20 to #187 per request.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777835461
OL,3,CTelecomms engineer paid foreigner to
OL,4,Cabuse children
OL,6,FHe would send specific instructions
OL,7,Fabout what he wanted and when the
OL,8,Fmaterial did not meet his expectations
OL,9,Fhe withheld payment until new media
OL,10,Fwas supplied.
OL,12,FHe told his contact to inflict sexual
OL,13,For physical harm, saying "it will be a
OL,14,Fgood money earn for you" and the child
OL,15,Fwould "get used" to it.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777835461
OL,3,CTelecomms engineer paid foreigner to
OL,4,Cabuse children
OL,6,FHe would also object to receiving
OL,7,Fcontent he had already seen, instead
OL,8,Fdemanding new images and videos of
OL,9,Fabuse. At one point he said he wanted
OL,10,Fto travel to the Philippines to abuse
OL,11,Fchildren himself.
OL,13,FRecords showed between June 2020 and
OL,14,FJune 2022, Beckett exchanged nearly
OL,15,F10,000 messages, 356 media files and
OL,16,F39 calls with the facilitator and paid
OL,17,Fjust under #560.
OL,19,FBeckett will be on the Sex Offenders
OL,20,FRegister for life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1777835461
OL,3,CTelecomms engineer paid foreigner to
OL,4,Cabuse children
OL,6,FJudge Simon Batiste described the
OL,7,Foffending as "vile, repulsive,
OL,8,Frevolting and truly appalling beyond
OL,9,Fwords".
OL,11,FMs Pownall added: "The transactional
OL,12,Frelationship between Beckett and the
OL,13,Ffacilitator exploited the victims'
OL,14,Fvulnerability and circumstances.
OL,16,F"With thanks to US law enforcement
OL,17,Fcolleagues and the Philippine National
OL,18,FPolice, the NCA was able to identify
OL,19,FBeckett and bring him to justice.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
